    answer:
      "Privacy is paramount in the music industry, and we take it seriously. All team members sign comprehensive confidentiality agreements and undergo thorough background checks. We never discuss our clients, their homes, or their schedules with anyone. As a veteran-owned business, we uphold the highest standards of integrity. Your privacy isn't just a policy - it's a commitment backed by our service record.",
  },
  {
    question: "Can you clean homes with home studios or recording equipment?",
    answer:
      "Yes, many of our Music Row clients have home studios, recording setups, or production rooms. We're experienced in carefully cleaning around expensive audio equipment, instruments, and studio furniture. We never touch mixing consoles, microphones, or equipment without explicit permission, and we use appropriate cleaning methods that won't damage sensitive electronics or acoustic treatments.",
  },
  {
    question:
      "Do you offer same-day cleaning for last-minute needs before tours or label visits?",
    answer:
      "Yes, we understand that music industry schedules can change rapidly. Whether you have a label executive visiting unexpectedly, need your home pristine before heading out on tour, or want to return from the road to a spotless space, we offer same-day service based on availability. Call us at 615-510-1427 as early as possible and we'll do our best to accommodate urgent requests.",
  },
  {
    question: "What areas near Music Row do you serve?",
