  {
    question: "Can you accommodate touring schedules and extended absences?",
    answer:
      "Absolutely. Many of our Music Row clients are touring artists or travel frequently for work. We can maintain your home while you're away, adjust service frequency during tour seasons, or provide a thorough deep clean before your return. We're experienced with key/code access, security systems, and maintaining empty homes to ensure everything is perfect when you get back.",
